disabling a security system.

3
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:07,750
Our initial situation is that we're
entering the home with the alarm set and

4
00:00:07,750 --> 00:00:10,370
we have two methods for
disabling the alarm.

5
00:00:10,370 --> 00:00:13,170
We can use the keypad or
we can use the keychain.

6
00:00:13,170 --> 00:00:16,378
Either way, our goal is that
we've entered the home and

7
00:00:16,378 --> 00:00:17,780
reenabled the alarm.

8
00:00:17,780 --> 00:00:20,294
Our selection rules might be something
like if we have our hands full,

9
00:00:20,294 --> 00:00:23,380
