can get inside and put the stuff down.

10
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:25,800
But if we don't have our hands full,
we'll use the keychain.

11
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:28,590
You might come up with other models for
this that have either different methods,

12
00:00:28,590 --> 00:00:30,830
different operators,
different selection rules.

13
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:33,890
